channel.title: How to multi-login on runescape
channel.description:
1) first open two runescape windows
[IMG]http://i118.photobucket.com/albums/o105/santaselfboy/1.jpg[/img]
2) click play runescape on both
[IMG]http://i118.photobucket.com/albums/o105/santaselfboy/2.jpg[/img]
3) on one window click high detail on the other goto the bottom of the page and select "unsigned applet" then click low detail
[IMG]http://i118.photobucket.com/albums/o105/santaselfboy/3.jpg[/img]
4)select the worlds you want on both
5) enter your usernames and passwords then click login
[IMG]http://i118.photobucket.com/albums/o105/santaselfboy/4.jpg[/img]
6) and thats it....
[IMG]http://i118.photobucket.com/albums/o105/santaselfboy/5.jpg[/img]
